OL,3,CArmy veteran calls on Chancellor to
OL,4,Cend to 'dementia tax' on budget day
OL,6,FSam Blackledge reports on calls for
OL,7,Fthe Chancellor to end a 'dementia tax'
OL,9,FAn Army veteran from Bridgwater whose
OL,10,Fwife lives with dementia is calling
OL,11,Ffor changes to taxes affecting home
OL,12,Fcare services.
OL,14,FMichael and Avril Staunton are
OL,15,Fsupported by The Filo Project, a non-
OL,16,Ffor-profit organisation providing
OL,17,Fgroup care days.
