OL,3,CArmy veteran calls on Chancellor to
OL,4,Cend to 'dementia tax' on budget day
OL,6,FMichael says the help it offers is a
OL,7,Flifeline for Avril, who suffers with
OL,8,FPosterior Cortical Atrophy, a rare
OL,9,Fform of dementia which affects her
OL,10,Fvision, spatial awareness and literacy.
OL,12,FBut users are charged 20% extra in VAT
OL,13,Fbecause of a tax anomaly.
OL,15,F"When you're with someone who has a
OL,16,Ffull-time disability like this, it
OL,17,Ftakes a lot of work and there's quite
OL,18,Fa lot of anxiety that goes with that,"
OL,19,FMichael told ITV West Country.
