OL,6,F"On top of that, there is less time to
OL,7,Flook after yourself. You really need
OL,8,Fsome little breaks, not just somebody
OL,9,Fcoming into your house or something
OL,10,Flike that.
OL,12,F"And Avril going off and doing
OL,13,Fsomething which is hers, that's really
OL,14,Fimportant."
OL,16,FAvril has been attending sessions
OL,17,Forganised by the Filo Project, a
OL,18,Fcommunity interest company which
OL,19,Fprovides small group care days across
OL,20,FDevon, Somerset and Cornwall.
