OL,3,CArmy veteran calls on Chancellor to
OL,4,Cend to 'dementia tax' on budget day
OL,6,FMichael said: "What Avril gains there
OL,7,Fis wonderful, she always comes back
OL,8,Freally happy, delighted."
OL,10,FHe added: "Within our communities,
OL,11,Fthere are really kind people. And so
OL,12,Fto be given that opportunity to do
OL,13,Fsomething in a very caring, loving way
OL,14,Fbrings a totally different dimension
OL,15,Fto this."
