OL,3,CArmy veteran calls on Chancellor to
OL,4,Cend to 'dementia tax' on budget day
OL,6,FLast week, Michael and Avril travelled
OL,7,Fto Westminster, along with
OL,8,Frepresentatives from the Filo Project,
OL,9,Fto present a letter to Chancellor
OL,10,FRachel Reeves asking her to use
OL,11,FWednesday's budget to exempt dementia
OL,12,Fservices from VAT.
OL,14,FLibby Price, from the Filo Project,
OL,15,Fsaid: "We are asking the Chancellor to
OL,16,Funderstand that putting VAT on
OL,17,Fsomething as fundamentally important
OL,18,Fas dementia support is wrong.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
