OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F439A1764184860
OL,3,CArmy veteran calls on Chancellor to
OL,4,Cend to 'dementia tax' on budget day
OL,6,F"VAT should not be a part of that
OL,7,Foffer. We need to support people to
OL,8,Flive well and to still have value. "
OL,10,FA Government spokesman said: "We are
OL,11,Fputting Britain at the forefront of
OL,12,Ftransforming treatment for dementia
OL,13,Fthrough continuing to fund high-
OL,14,Fquality research into the disease and
OL,15,Fensuring new clinically and cost-
OL,16,Feffective treatments are rolled out in
OL,17,Fa safe and timely way."
